# DevBoard

A full-stack project management tool with Kanban board.

## Live Demo
https://devboard-pied.vercel.app

## Tech Stack
- **Frontend**: React, Tailwind CSS, Vite — deployed on Vercel
- **Backend**: FastAPI, SQLAlchemy, SQLite
- **Auth**: JWT authentication with bcrypt password hashing

## Features
- User registration and login
- Create and manage projects
- Kanban board with To Do / In Progress / Done columns
- JWT protected REST API with 15+ endpoints

## Run Locally

### Backend
```bash
cd backend
pip install -r requirements.txt
uvicorn main:app --reload
```

### Frontend
```bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev
```
